hadiths[61]{hadithnumber,text}:
391,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Namaze Zohar mein khadey ho gaey jabke aap ko bethna tha, chunanche jab namaz puri kar chukey to salam pherney sey pehley aap ney usi jagah bethey bethey do sajdey kiye , aap ney har sajdey mein Allahu-Akbar kaha , aur aap key sath logon ney bhi sajde sahoo kiye. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ibn Buhena ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi hadees aai hai. 3- Muhammad bin Ibrahim sey riwayat ki hai ke Abu-Hurera aur Abdullah bin Saaib Qaari Raziallahu anhuma dono sahoo key dono sajdey salam sey pehley kartey they. 4- aur isi par baaz ehle-ilm ka amal hai aur Shafai ka bhi yehi qol hai, un ki raey hai ke sajda saho har surat mein salam sey pehley hai, aur ye hadees dusri hadeeson ko khatm karne waali hai. kyonkey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka amal aakhir mein isi par raha hai. 5- aur Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain ke jab aadmi do rakat key baad khada ho jaey to wo ibne Buhena (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees par amal kartey huye sajda sahoo salam sey pehley karey. 6- Ali bin Madeeni kehtey hain ke Abdullah ibne Buhena hi Abdullah bin Malik hain, ibn Buhena key baap Malik hain aur Buhena un ki maa hain. 7- sajda sahoo ke barey mein ehle-ilm ke maa-bain ikhtilaf hai ke usey aadmi salam sey pehley karey ya salam key baad. baaz logon ki raey hai ke isey salam key baad karey, ye qol Sufiyan Sory aur ehle-koofa ka hai. 8- aur baaz logon ney kaha hai ke isey salam sey pehley karey yehi qol aksar fuqaha Madina ka hai, maslan Yahya bin Saeed , Rabeea waghera ka aur yehi qol Shafai ka bhi hai, 9- aur baaz log kehtey hain ke jab namaz mein ziyadti hui ho to salam key baad karey aur jab kami reh gaee ho to salam sey pehley karey, yehi qol Malik bin Anas ka hai. 10- aur Ahmed kehtey hain ke jis surat mein jis tarah par sajda sahoo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi (riwayat hua) hai us surat mein isi tarah sajda sahoo karna chahiye, wo kehtey hain ke jab do rakat ke baad khada ho jaey to ibne Buhena (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees ke mutabiq salam sey pehley sajda karey aur jab Zohar paanch rakat padh ley to wo sajda sahoo salam key baad karey , aur agar Zohar aur Asr mein do hi rakat mein salam pher dey to aisi surat mein salam key baad sajda sahoo karey, isi tarah jis jis surat mein jaisey jaisey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka amal mojud hai, is par isi tarah amal karey, aur sahoo ki jis surat mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey koi amal marvi na (riwayat na hui) ho to is mein sajda sahoo salam sey pehley karey.  11- Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi Ahmed ke muwaafiq kehtey hain. magar farq itna hai ke wo kehtey hain ke sahoo ki jis surat mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey koi amal mojud na ho to is mein agar namaz mein ziyadti hui ho to salam key baad sajda sahoo karey aur agar kami hui ho to salam sey pehley karey."
392,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Zohar paanch rakat padhi to aap sey puchha gaya : kya namaz badha di gaee hai?  yani chaar ke bajaey paanch rakat kar di gaee hai) to aap ne salam pherney key baad do sajdey kiye. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
393,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney sahoo key dono sajdey baat karney key baad kiye. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai padhi. , padhi. 2- is bab mein Muawiya , Abdullah bin Jaafar aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
394,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney saho key dono sajdey salam key baad kiye. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- (abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ki) ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- usey Ayub aur deegar kaee logon ney bhi ibn Sirin sey riwayat kya hai, 3- ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 4- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, wo kehtey hain ke jab aadmi Zohar bhool kar paanch rakat padh ley to uski namaz durust hai wo saho key do sajdey kar ley agar-che wo chauthi (rakat) mein na betha ho, yehi Shafai, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai, 5- aur baaz log kehtey hain ke jab Zohar paanch rakat padh ley aur chauthi rakat mein na betha ho to uski namaz faasid ho jaeygi. ye qol Sufiyan Sory aur baaz koofiyon ka hai."
395,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen namaz padhaai aap sey saho ho gaya, to aap ney do sajdey kiye phir tashahud padha , phir salam phera. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- Abdul-Wahab saqafii, Hushem aur unkey ilawa kaee aur logon ney b-tareeq : «Khalid Haza an abi Qalaba» ye hadees zara lambey siyaaq key sath riwayat ki hai, aur wo yehi Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Asr mein sirf teen hi rakat padh kar salam pher diya to eik aadmi utha jisey « kharbaaq » kaha jata tha (aur usney puchha : kya namaz mein kami kar di gaee hai, ya aap bhool gaey hain) 3- sajda saho key tashahud key silsiley mein ehle-ilm key darmyan ikhtilaf hai. baaz kehtey hain ke sajda saho key baad tashahud padheyga aur salam phereyga. aur baaz kehtey ke sajda saho mein tashahud aur salam nahin hai aur jab salam sey pehley sajda saho karey to tashahud na padhey, yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai ke jab salam sey pehley sajda saho karey to tashahud na padhey (ikhtilaf to salam key baad mein hai )."
396,"mainey abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : hum mein sey koi namaz padhta hai aur ye nahin janta ke usney kitni rakat padhi hain (ya wo kya kerey?) to abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya hai : '' jab tum mein sey koi shakhs namaz padhey aur ye na jaan sakey ke kitni padhi hai? to wo bethey bethey saho key do sajdey kar ley''. (yaqeeni baat par bana karney key baad) Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Usman , ibne-Masood , Aaisha , Abu-Hurera waghera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- ye hadees abu-Saeed sey deegar kaee sanadon sey bhi marvi hai, 4- Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ye bhi marvi hai ke aap ney farmaya : '' jab tum sey kisi ko eik aur do mein shak ho jaey to usey eik hi maaney aur jab do aur teen mein shak ho to usey do maaney aur salam pherney sey pehley saho key do sajdey karey ''. usi par hamarey as-haab ( muhaddeseen (ka amal hai padhi. aur baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke jab kisi ko apni namaz mein shubha ho jaey aur wo na jaan sakey ke usney kitni rakat padhi hain? to wo phir sey lotaye padhi. ."
397,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' aadmi key paas shetan uski namaz mein aata hai aur usey shubha mein dal deta hai, yahan tak aadmi nahin jaan paata ke usney kitni rakat padhi hain? chunanche tum mein sey kisi ko agar is qism ka shubha mehsus ho to usey chahiye ke wo bethey bethey saho key do sajdey kar ley '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
398,"mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko ye farmatey huye suna : '' jab koi shakhs namaz bhool jaey aur ye na jaan sakey ke usney eik rakat padhi hai ya do ? to aisi surat mein usey eik maaney , aur agar wo ye na ja sakey ke usney do padhi hai ya teen to aisi surat mein do par bina kerey. aur agar wo ye na jaan sakey ke usney teen padhi hai ya chaar to teen par bina kerey. aur salam pherney sey pehley saho key do sajdey kar ley''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ye hadees Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) sey aur bhi sanadon sey marvi hai."
399,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam (zohar ya Asr ki) do rakat padh kar (muqtadiyon ki taraf) paltey to zul-yadain ney aap sey puchha : Allah key Rasool ! kya namaz kam kar di gaee hai ya aap bhool gaey hain? to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney puchha : '' kya zul-yadain sach keh rahey hain?'' logon ney arz kya : haan (aap ney do hi rakat padhi hain) to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam khadey huye aur aakhiri dono rakatein padhein phir salam pheraa, phir Allahu-akbar kaha, phir apney pehley sajda ki tarah ya us sey kuch lamba sajda kya, phir Allahu-akbar kaha aur sar uthaya, phir apney usi sajda ki tarah ya us sey kuch lamba sajda kya. (yani sajda saho kya) Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Imran bin Husain , ibne-Umar , zul-yadain (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- is hadees key barey mein ehle-ilm key beech ikhtilaf hai. baaz ehle-koofa kehtey hain ke jab koi namaz mein bhool kar ya la-ilmi mein ya kisi bhi wajeh sey baat kar bethey to usey naey sirey sey namaz dohrani hogi. wo is hadees mein mazkur waqiey ki taaweel ye kartey hain ke ye waqia namaz mein baat cheet karney ki hurmat sey pehley ka hai, 4- rahey Imam Shafai to unhoney is hadees ko sahih jana hai aur usi key mutabiq unhoney fatwa diya hai, unka kehna hai ke ye hadees is hadees sey ziyada sahih hai jo rozey daar key silsiley mein marvi hai ke jab wo bhool kar kha ley to is par rozey ki qaza nahin, kyonkey wo Allah ka diya huwa rizq hai. Shafai kehtey hain ke un logon ney rozey daar key qasdan aur bhool kar khaney mein jo tafriq ki hai wo Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees ki wajeh sey hai, 5- Imam Ahmed Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees key mutalliq kehtey hain ke agar Imam ye samajh kar ke uski namaz puri ho chuki hai koi baat kar ley phir usey malum ho ke uski namaz puri nahin hui hai to wo apni namaz puri kar ley, aur jo Imam key peechey muqtadi ho aur baat kar ley aur ye janta ho ke abhi kuch namaz uskey zimma baqi hai to is par lazim hai ke wo usey dobara padhey, unhoney is baat sey daleel pakdi hai ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamaney mein faraaiz kam ya ziyada kiye ja saktey they. aur zul-yadain (Raziallahu anhu) ney jo baat ki thi to wo mehaz us wajeh sey ke unhen yaqin tha ke namaz kamil ho chuki hai aur ab kisi key liye is tarah baat karna jayez nahin jo zul-yadain key liye jayez ho gaya tha, kyonkey ab faraaiz mein kami beshi nahin ho sakti padhi. , 6- Ahmed ka qol bhi kuch usi sey milta-julta hai, Is-haq bin Raahviya ney bhi is baab mein Ahmed jaisi baat kahi hai."
400,"mainey Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : kya Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apney jooton mein namaz padhtey they? to unhoney kaha : haan padhtey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Masood , Abdullah bin abi Habiba, Abdullah bin Amr , Amr bin Hures , Shaddad bin Aus Saqafi, Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) aur Ata sey bhi jo bani Sheeba key eik fard they ahadees aai hain, 3- aur usi par ehle-ilm ka amal hai."
401,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Fajr aur maghrib mein qunoot padhtey they padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Bara ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali , Anas , Abu-Hurera , ibne-Abbas , aur khafaaf bin Ema bin Rahza Ghifaari (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- Fajr mein qunoot padhney key silsiley mein ehle-ilm key darmiyan ikhtilaf hai. Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ki raey Fajr mein qunoot padhney ki hai, yehi Malik aur Shafai ka qol hai, 4- Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain ke Fajr mein qunoot na padhey, illa ye ke musalmanon par koi musibat nazil hui ho to aisi surat mein Imam ko chahiye ke musalmanon key lashkar key liye dua kerey."
402,"mainey apney baap ( Tariq bin Ashim (Raziallahu anhu)) sey arz kya : abba jaan ! aap ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) , abu-Bakar , umr aur Usman (Raziallauh anhum) key peechey namaz padhi hai aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key peechey bhi yahan koofa mein taqriban paanch baras tak padhi hai, kya ye log ( barabar ( qunoot (Qunoote-Nazila) padhtey they? to unhoney kaha : merey betey ! ye bid-at hai padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. aur Sufiyan Sory kehtey hain ke agar Fajr mein qunoot padhey to bhi achcha hai aur agar na padhey to bhi achcha hai, wesay unhoney pasand usi baat ko kya hai ke na padhey aur ibne-Mubarak Fajr mein qunoot padhney ko durust nahin samajhtey."
403,isi sanad sey usi mafhoom ki isi tarah ki hadees riwayat ki.
404,"mainey Rasool akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key peechey namaz padhi , mujhey chheenk aai to mainey « الحمد لله حمدا كثيرا طيبا مباركا فيه مباركا عليه كما يحب ربنا ويرضى » kaha jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) namaz padh kar paltey to aap ney puchha : '' namaz mein kon bol raha tha? '' to kisi ney jawab nahin diya, phir aap ney yehi baat dobara poochhii ke '' namaz mein kon bol raha tha? '' is baar bhi kisi ney koi jawab nahin diya, phir aap ney yehi baat teesri baar poochhi ke '' namaz mein kon bol raha tha? ''Rifaa bin Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kya : main tha Allah key Rasool ! aap ney puchha : ''tum ney kya kaha tha? '' unhoney kaha : yun kaha tha « الحمد لله حمدا كثيرا طيبا مباركا فيه مباركا عليه كما يحب ربنا ويرضى » to Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ke tees sey zayed farishtey is par jhaptey ke usey kon ley kar aasman par chadhey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Rifaa ki hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Anas, Wayl bin Hajar aur Aamir bin Rabee (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- baaz ehle-ilm key nazdik ye waqia nafl ka hai padhi. isliye ke Tabe-een mein sey kaee logon ka kehna hai ke jab aadmi farz namaz mein chheenkey to Alhamdulillah apney ji mein kahey us sey ziyada ki un logon ney ijazat nahin di."
405,"hum Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key peechey namaz mein baat cheet kar liya kartey they, aadmi apney sath waley sey baat kar liya karta tha, yahan tak ke aayate-karima : « ‏وقوموا لله قانتين » '' Allah key liye baa adab khadey raha karo '' nazil hui to hamen khamosh rehney ka hukm diya gaya aur baat karney sey rok diya gaya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Masood aur Muawiya bin Hakam Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- aksar ehle-ilm ka amal isi par hai ke aadmi namaz mein qasdan ya bhool kar guftgu kar ley to namaz dohraaey. Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak aur ehle-koofa ka yehi qol hai. aur baaz ka kehna hai ke jab namaz mein qasdan guftgu karey to namaz dohraaey aur agar bhool sey ya la-ilmi mein guftgu ho jaey to namaz kafi hogi, 4- Shafai isi key qaail hain."
406,"mainey Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey suna : main jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey koi hadees sunta to Allah us sey mujhey nafa pahunchata , jitna wo pahunchana chahta. aur jab aap key as-haab mein sey koi aadmi mujh sey bayan karta to main us sey qism leta. ( kya waqae tum ney ye hadees Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey khud suni hai?) jab wo merey samney qism kha leta to main uski tasdeeq karta, mujh sey abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan kya aur abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney sach bayan kya ke mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : '' jo shakhs gunah karta hai, phir ja kar wuzu karta hai phir namaz padhta hai, phir Allah sey istighfar karta hai to Allah usey maaf kar deta hai. phir aap ney ye aayat padhi « والذين إذا فعلوا فاحشة والذين إذا فعلوا فاحشة أو ظلموا أنفسهم ذكروا الله فاستغفروا لذنوبهم ومن يغفر الذنوب إلا الله ولم يصروا على ما فعلوا وهم يعلمون ''aur jab un sey koi nashaista harkat ya koi gunah sarzad ho jata hai to wo Allah ko yad kar key fauran istighfar kartey hain. aur Allah key siwa kon gunah bakhsh sakta hai, aur wo jaan-boojh kar kisi gunah par adey nahin rehtey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai, hum isey sirf usi tareeq sey yani Usman bin Mughira hi ki sanad sey jantey hain, 2- aur un sey Shoba aur doosrey aur logon ney bhi riwayat ki hai un logon ney isey abu-Awaana ki hadees ki tarah marfooan riwayat kya hai, aur usey Sufiyan Sory aur musair ney bhi riwayat kya hai lekin un dono ki riwayat maqoof hai marfoo nahin aur musair sey ye hadees marfooan bhi marvi hai aur siwaye is hadees key Asma bin Hakam ki kisi aur marfoo hadees ka hamen ilm nahin, padhi. 3- is bab mein ibne-Masood , abu Darda, Anas , abu-Umama , Muaz , Waasila, aur abul-Yusr Kaab bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
407,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''saat baras key bachey ko namaz sikhaao, aur das baras key bachey ko namaz na padhney par maaro''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Sabra bin Maabad Johni (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain, unka kehna hai ke '' jo ladka das baras key ho janey key baad namaz chhodey wo uski qaza karey"
408,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' jab aadmi ko salam pherney sey pehley « hadas » laahiq ho jaey aur wo apni namaz key bilkul aakhir mein yani qaada Akhira mein beth chuka ho to uski namaz durust hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ki sanad koi khas qawi nahin, iski sanad mein iztirab hai, 2- Abdur-Rehman bin Ziyad bin Anam, jo Afriqi hain ko baaz muhaddeseen ney zaeef qarar diya hai. un mein Yahya bin Saeed Qataan aur Ahmed bin Hanbal bhi shamil hain, 3- baaz ehle-ilm usi taraf gaey hain. wo kehtey hain ke jab koi tashahud ki miqdaar key barabar beth chuka ho aur salam pherney sey pehley usey «hadas» laahiq ho jaey to phir uski namaz puri ho qaee, 4- aur baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke jab « hadas » tashahud padhney sey ya salam pherney sey pehley laahiq ho jaey to namaz dohraaey. Shafai ka yehi qol hai, 5- aur Ahmed kehtey hain : jab wo tashahud na padhey aur salam pher dey to uski namaz usey kafi ho jaeygi, isliye ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka irshad hai : « وتحليلها التسليم » yani namaz mein jo cheezen haram hui thin salam pherney hi sey halal hoti hain, baghair salam key namaz sey nahin nikla ja sakta aur tashahud itna aham nahin jitna salam hai ke uskey tarak sey namaz durust na hogi , eik baar Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) do rakat key baad khadey ho gaey apni namaz jari rakhi aur tashahud nahin kya, 6- Is-haq bin Ibrahim bin Raahviya kehtey hain : jab tashahud kar ley aur salam na pheraa ho to namaz ho gaee , unhoney ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees sey istidlaal kya hai ke jis waqt Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney unhen tashahud sikhaya to farmaya : jab tum us sey farigh ho gaey to tum ney apna fariza pura kar liya."
409,"hum log Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key sath eik safar mein they ke barish honey lagi to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' jo chahey apney derey main hi namaz padh ley ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar , Samra, abu Maleeh, Aamir ( jinhoney apney baap Usama bin umr Hazl sey riwayat ki hai) aur Abdur-Rehman bin Samra (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- baaz ehle-ilm ney barish aur keechad mein jamaat mein hazir na honey ki rukhsat di hai, yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain."
410,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key paas kuch faqir o mohtaj log aaye aur kaha : Allah key Rasool ! maaldaar namaz padhtey hain jaisey hum padhtey hain wo roza rakhtey hain jaisey hum rakhtey hain. unkey paas maal bhi hai, us sey wo ghulam azad kartey aur sadqa detey hain? aap ney farmaya : '' jab tum namaz padh chuko to tentees martaba '' subhan Allah '' , tentees martaba '' الحمد لله '' aur tentees martaba '' الله أكبر '' aur das martaba ''la ila-h illallah'' keh liya karo, to tum un logon ko paa logey jo tum par sabqat ley gaey hain, aur jo tum sey peechey hain wo tum par sabqat na ley ja sakengey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Kaab bin Ajra , Anas , Abdullah bin Amr , Zaid bin Sabit , Abu-Darda, ibne-Umar aur Abu-Zar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, neez is baab mein Abu-Hurera aur Mughira Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey ye bhi marvi hai ke aap ney farmaya : '' do aadatein hain jinhen jo bhi musalman aadmi baja layega jannat mein dakhil hoga. eik ye ke wo har namaz key baad das baar '' Subhanallah '' , das baar ''Alhamdulillah'', das baar ''Allahu-akbar'' kahey, doosrey ye ke wo apney sotey waqt tentees martaba '' Subhanallah '' , tentees martaba '' الحمد لله '' aur chauntees martaba '' الله أكبر '' kahey."
411,"wo log eik safar mein Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key sath they, wo eik tang jagah pahunchey they ke namaz ka waqt aa gaya, ooper sey barish honey lagi , aur nichey keechad ho qaee, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney apni sawari hi par Azan di aur iqaamat kahi aur sawari hi par aagey badhey aur unhen namaz padhaai , aap ishara sey namaz padhtey they, sajdey mein rukoo sey qadrey ziyada jhuktey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, umr bin Rumaah Balkhi uskey riwayat karney mein munfarid hain. ye sirf unhin ki sanad sey jaani jati hai. aur un sey ye hadees ehle-ilm mein sey kaee logon ney riwayat ki hai, 2- Anas bin Malik sey bhi isi tarah marvi hai ke unhoney pani aur keechad main apni sawari par namaz padhi, 3- aur usi par ehle-ilm ka amal hai. Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi yehi kehtey hain."
412,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney namaz padhi yahan tak ke aap key pair sooj gaey to aap sey arz kya gaya : kya aap aisi zahmat kartey hain halanke aap key agley pichley tamam gunah bakhsh diye gaey hain? to aap ney farmaya : ''kya main shukar guzar banda na banon?'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera aur Aaisha Raziallahu anhuma sey ahadees aai hain."
413,"main Madiney aaya : mainey kaha : aey Allah mujhey nek aur Saleh sathi nasib farma , chunanche Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key paas bethna muyassar ho gaya, mainey un sey kaha : mainey Allah sey dua maangi thi ke mujhey nek sathi ata farma , to aap mujh sey koi aisi hadees bayan kijiye , jisey aap ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey suni ho, shayad Allah mujhey us sey faeyda pahunchaey , unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : '' qiyamat key roz bandey sey sab sey pehley uski namaz ka muhaasba hoga, agar wo theek rahi to kamiyab ho gaya, aur agar wo kharab nikli to wo nakam aur na-murad raha, aur agar uski farz namazon mein koi kami padhi. hogi to rab taala ( farishton sey) farmaeyga : dekho , merey us bandey key paas koi nafl namaz hai? chunanche farz namaz ki kami ki talafi us nafl sey kar di jaeygi, phir usi andaz sey sarey aamal ka muhaasba hoga ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai, 2- ye hadees deegar aur sanadon sey bhi Abu-Hurera sey riwayat ki gaee hai, 3- Hasan key baaz talaamiza ney Hasan sey aur unhoney Qabisa bin Hures sey is hadees key ilawa dusri aur hadisein bhi riwayat ki hain aur mashhoor Qabisa bin Hures hi hai padhi. , ye hadees b-tareeq : « Anas bin Hakim an abi Hurera an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » bhi riwayat ki gaee hai, 4- is bab mein Tameem daari (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
414,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' jo baara rakat sunnat padhi. par madawmat kerega (hamesha padhega) Allah uskey liye jannat main eik ghar banaeyga : chaar rakatein Zohar sey pehley padhi. , do rakatein uskey baad , do rakatein maghrib key baad , do rakatein Isha key baad aur do rakatein Fajr sey pehley ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees is sanad sey gharib hai, 2- sanad mein Mughira bin Ziyad par baaz ehle-ilm ney unkey hifz key talluq sey kalam kya hai, 3- is bab mein Umme-Habiba , Abu-Hurera , abu-Musa aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
415,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs raat aur din mein baara rakat sunnat padheyga, uskey liye jannat main eik ghar banaya jaeyga : chaar rakatein Zohar sey pehley , do rakatein uskey baad, do maghrib key baad , do Isha key baad aur do Fajr sey pehley ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : anbasaa ki hadees jo Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu Anha) sey marvi hai is baab mein Hasan sahih hai. aur wo anbasaa sey deegar aur sanadon sey bhi marvi hai."
416,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' Fajr ki dono rakatein duniya aur duniya mein jo kuch hai un sab sey behtar hain ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali , ibne-Umar , aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. jinhen Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) un mein padhtey they."
417,"mein Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko eik mahiney tak dekhta raha , Fajr sey pehley ki dono rakaaton mein aap « قل يا أيها الكافرون » aur « ‏قل هو الله أحد‏ » padhtey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan hai, 2- aur hum sura ki riwayat ko jisey unhoney Abu-Is'haq sey riwayat ki hai sirf abu-Ahmad Zubairi hi key tareeq sey jantey hain, ( jabke ( logon ( muhaddeseen ( key nazdik maroof « an Israail an abi Is-haq» hai bajaey « Sufiyan abi Is-haq » key, 3- aur abu-Ahmad Zubairi key wastey sey bhi Israel sey riwayat ki gaee hai, 4- abu-Ahmad Zubairi Suqa aur Hafiz hain, mainey Bundaar ko kehtey suna hai ke mainey abu-Ahmad Zubairi sey ziyada achey hafizey wala nahin dekha , abu-Ahmad ka naam Muhammad bin Abdullah bin Zuber koofii Asadi hai, 5- is bab mein ibne-Masood , Anas , Abu-Hurera , ibne-Abbas , Hafsa aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
418,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Fajr ki do rakatein padh chuktey aur agar aap ko mujh sey koi kaam hota to (us barey mein) mujh sey guftgu farma letey , warna namaz key liye nikal jatey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ney Fajr key tulu honey baad sey ley kar Fajr padhney tak guftgu karna makrooh qarar diya hai, siwaye uskey ke wo guftgu zikre-Ilahi sey mutalliq ho ya bahut zaruri ho, aur yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai."
419,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' tulue-Fajr key baad siwaye do rakat (sunnat Fajr) key koi namaz nahin ''. is hadees ka matlab ye hai ke tulu Fajr key baad) farz sey pehley ( siwaye do rakat sunnat key aur koi namaz nahin . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar ki hadees gharib hai, usey hum sirf Qudama bin Musa hi key tareeq sey jantey hain aur un sey kaee logon ney riwayat ki hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr aur Hafsa (Raziallauh anhum) sey ahadees aai hain, 3- aur yehi qol hai jis par ehle-ilm ka ijmaa hai : unhoney tulu Fajr key baad) farz sey pehley ( siwaye Fajr ki dono sunnaton key koi aur namaz padhney ko makrooh qarar diya hai padhi. ."
420,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' jab tum mein sey koi Fajr ki do rakat ( sunnat ( padhey to daain karwat par letey '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi marvi hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Fajr ki dono rakatein apney ghar mein padhtey to apni daain karwat let'tey , 4- baaz ehle-ilm ki raey hai ke aisa istehbaban kya jaey."
421,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab jamaat khadi ho jaey padhi. to farz namaz padhi. ke siwa koi namaz  (jayez) nahin.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai. 2- isi tarah eik dusri sanad sey bhi Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai. 3- is bab mein ibne Buhena , Abdullah bin Amr , Abdullah bin Sarjis , ibne-Abbas aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 4- aur Hammad bin Zaid aur Sufiyan bin Uena ney bhi Amr bin Dinar sey riwayat ki hai lekin un dono ney isey marfoo nahin kiya hai aur marfoo hadees hi hamarey nazdik ziyada sahih hai. 5- Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya isi key qaail hain. 6- iskey ilawa aur (eik teesri) sanad sey bhi ye hadees ba-wasta Abu-Hurera Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai. aur unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai. (jaisey) Ayash bin Abbas Qatbaani Misri abu-Salma sey, aur abu-Salma ney Abu-Hurera sey aur Abu-Hurera ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai."
422,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam nikley aur jamaat key liye iqaamat keh di gaee , to mainey aap key sath Fajr padhi , phir Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam paltey to mujhey dekha ke main namaz padhney ja raha hun, to aap ney farmaya : ''Qais zara thehro, kya do namazein eik sath padhi. (padhney ja rahey ho?) ''maine arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! mainey Fajr ki dono sunnatein nahin padhi thin۔ aap ney farmaya : ''tab koi harj nahin.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- hum Muhammad bin Ibrahim ki hadees ko uskey jaisi sirf Saad bin Saeed hi key tareeq sey jantey hain, 2- Sufiyan bin Uena kehtey hain ke Ata bin abi Ribah ney bhi ye hadees Saad bin Saeed sey suni hai. 3- ye hadees mursalan (wo hadees jismein taabaee se upar raavi ka naam milta ho) bhi riwayat ki jati hai. 4- ehale Makka mein sey kuchh logon ney isi hadees key mutabiq kaha hai ke aadmi key Fajr ki farz namaz padhney key baad suraj nikalney sey pehley dono sunnatein padhney mein koi harj nahin. 5- Saad bin Saeed Yahya bin Saeed Ansari ke bhai hain, aur Qais Yahya bin Saeed Ansari ke dada hain. unhen Qais bin Amr bhi kaha jata hai aur Qais bin Qahad bhi. 6- is hadees ki sanad muttasil nahin hai. Muhammad bin Ibrahim Temi ney Qais sey nahin suna hai, baaz logon ney ye hadees Saad bin Saeed sey aur Saad ney Muhammad bin Ibrahim sey riwayat ki hai ke ''nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam nikley to Qais ko dekha.''  aur ye abdul-Azeez ki hadees sey jisey unhoney Saad bin Saeed sey riwayat ki hai ziyada sahih hai."
423,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo Fajr ki dono sunnatein na padh sakey to unhen suraj nikalney key baad padh ley.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees hum sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- ibne-Umar sey ye bhi riwayat ki gaee hai ke unhoney aisa kiya hai. 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi isi key qaail hain. 4- hum kisi aisey shakhs ko nahin jantey jisney Hamaam sey ye hadees is sanad sey is tarah riwayat ki ho siwaye Amr bin Aasim Kilaabi key. aur b-tareeq : (Qataada an Nazar bin Anas an Bashir bin Naheek an abi Huraira an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) mash'hoor ye hai ke aap ney farmaya : ''jisney Fajr ki eik rakat bhi suraj tulu honey sey pehley pa li to usne Fajr pa li.''"
424,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Zohar sey pehley chaar rakatein aur uskey baad do rakatein padhtey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Aaisha Raziallahu anhuma aur Umme-Habiba Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- hum sey abu-Bakar Attaar ney bayan kiya hai wo kehtey hain ke Ali bin Abdullah ney Yahya bin Saeed sey aur Yahya ney Sufiyan sey riwayat ki hai ke wo kehtey they ke hum jantey they ke aiAasim bin Zamra ki hadees Haris  (Aa'war) ki hadees sey afzal hai. 4- Sahaba kiram aur baad key logon mein sey aksar ehal ka amal isi par hai. wo ba-sand kartey hain ke aadmi Zohar sey pehley chaar rakatein padhey۔ aur yehi Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak , Is-haq bin Raahviya aur ehle-koofa ka bhi qol hai. aur baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke din aur raat (dono) ki namazein do do rakatein hain, wo har do rakat key baad fasal (gaip) karney key qaail hain Shafai aur Ahmed bhi yehi kehtey hain."
425,mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath Zohar sey pehley do rakatein padhi. aur uskey baad do rakatein padhin. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aur Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 2- ibne-Umar ki hadees Hasan sahih hai.
426,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab Zohar sey pehley chaar rakatein na padh paatey to unhen aap uskey baad padhtey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- hum isey ibne-Mubarak ki hadees sey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. aur isey Qais bin Rabee ney Shoba sey aur Shoba ney Khalid  sey isi tarah riwayat kiya hai. aur hum Qais bin Rabee key ilawa kisi aur ko nahin jantey jisney Shoba sey riwayat ki ho. 3- b-atareeq : (Abdur-Rehman bin abi Lela an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) bhi isi tarah (mursalan) marvi (riwayat hui) hai.
427,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney Zohar sey pehley chaar rakatein aur Zohar key baad chaar rakatein padhein Allah usey jahannam ki aag par haram kar dega.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- aur ye is sanad key ilawa dusri sanadon sey bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai.
428,"mainey apni behan Ummul-momenin Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu Anha) ko kehtey suna ke mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna hai ke jisney Zohar sey pehley ki chaar rakaaton aur uskey baad ki chaar rakaaton par muhaafizat ki to Allah us ko jahannam ki aag par haram kar dega. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- Qasim darasal Abdur-Rehman ke betey hain. unki kunniyat abu-Abdur-Rehman hai, wo Abdur-Rehman bin Khalid bin Yazeed bin Muawiya key Mola aur bharosemand hain, Sham ke rehney waley aur abu-Umama ke shagrid hain."
429,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Asr sey pehley chaar rakatein padhtey they, aur unke darmiyan : muqarrab farishton aur un musalmanon aur mominon par ke jinhon-ne unki taabedari ki un par salam key zariey fasal (gap) kartey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai. padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. Is-haq bin Ibrahim ( ibne Raahviya ( ney Asr sey pehley ki chaar rakaaton mein fasal (gap) na karney ko tarjeeh di hai, aur unhoney isi hadees sey daleel di hai. Is-haq kehtey hain : un ke (Ali ke) qol ''salam ke zariey in ke darmiyan fasal (gap) karney'' key maana ye hain ke aap do rakat key baad tashahud padhtey they, aur Shafai aur Ahmed ki raey hai ke raat aur din ki namaz do-do rakat hai aur wo dono Asr sey pehley ki chaar rakaaton mein salam key zariey fasal (gap) karney ko pasand kartey hain."
430,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah taala us shakhs par reham karey jisney Asr sey pehley chaar rakatein padhin.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib Hasan hai.
431,"Main shumar nahin kar sakta ke mainey kitni baar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko maghrib key baad ki dono rakaaton mein aur Fajr sey pehley ki dono rakaaton mein « قل يا أيها الكافرون » aur « ‏‏قل هو الله أحد » padhtey suna padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, 2- ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf « Abdullah bin Maadaan an Aasim » hi key tareeq sey jantey hain."
432,"Mainey maghrib ke baad dono rakatein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath aap ke ghar mein padhin. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Raafey bin khadij aur Kaab bin Ajra Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
433,"Mujhey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey das rakatein yad hain jinhen aap raat aur din mein padha kartey they : do rakatein Zohar sey pehley padhi. , do uskey baad , do rakatein maghrib key baad , aur do rakatein Isha key baad , aur mujh sey Hafsa (Raziallahu Anha) ney bayan kiya hai ke aap Fajr sey pehley do rakatein padhtey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
434,"ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey isi ke jaisi riwayat hai, Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
435,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney maghrib key baad chhe rakatein padhein aur unkey darmiyan koi buri baat na ki, to unka sawab baara saal ki ibadat key barabar hoga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat karti hain ke aap ney farmaya : ''jisney maghrib key baad bees rakatein padhein Allah uskey liye jannat main eik ghar banaeyga.''  2- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf (Zaid bin Hubaab an umr bin abi Khas'am) ki sanad sey jantey hain.  3- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna ke umr bin Abdullah bin abi Khasam hadees ke munkir hain. aur unhoney unhen sakht zaeef kaha hai."
436,"Mainey Ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki namaz key barey mein puchha to unhoney bataya ke aap Zohar sey pehley do rakatein padhtey they, aur uskey baad do rakatein, maghrib key baad do rakatein , Isha key baad do rakatein aur Fajr sey pehley do rakatein padhtey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Ali aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 2- Abdullah bin Shaqeeq ki hadees jisey wo Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey riwayat kartey hain, Hasan sahih hai."
437,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : raat ki nafli namaz do do rakat hai, jab tumhen namaze Fajr ka waqt ho janey ka dar ho to eik rakat padh kar usey witr bana lo, aur apni aakhiri namaz witr rakho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Amr bin Abasa (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- isi par ehle-ilm ka amal hai ke raat ki namaz do do rakat hai, Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi yehi qol hai."
438,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''ramzan ke baad sab sey afzal rozey Allah ke mahiney Mohrram ke rozey hain aur farz namaz ke baad sab sey afzal namaz raat ki namaz (tahajjud) hai.''
439,"Unhoney Ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey puchha : Ramzan mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki namaze tahajjud kaisi hoti thi? kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam tahajjud Ramzan mein aur ghair Ramzan giyara rakat sey ziyada nahin padhtey they, aap (do-do kar ke) chaar rakatein is khoobi, khoobsurti se ada farmatey ke unke Husn aur tawaalat (lambaai) ko na poochho, phir mazeed chaar rakatein (do-do kar key) padhtey, unkey Husn aur tawaalat ko bhi na poochho, phir teen rakatein padhtey. Ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) bayan karti hain ke mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! kya aap witr padhney sey pehley so jatey hain? farmaya : ''Aaisha ! meri aankhen soti hain, dil nahin sota.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
440,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam raat ko giyara rakatein padhtey they un mein sey eik rakat witr hoti. to jab aap us sey farigh ho jatey to apney daain karwat let'tey.
441,Ibne Shahab sey isi tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
442,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam raat ko tehra rakatein padhtey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Abu-Hamza Zab'ee ka naam Nasar bin Imran Zab'ee hai.
443,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam raat ko nau rakatein padhtey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , Zaid bin Khalid aur Fazal bin Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
444,"ye hadees isi tarah Aamash sey riwayat ki hai, hum sey isey Mehmood bin Ghelaan ney bayan kiya, wo kehtey hain ke hum sey Yahya bin Adam ney bayan kiya aur unhoney Sufiyan sey aur Sufiyan ney Aamash sey riwayat ki. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : raat ki namaz key silsiley mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ziyada sey ziyada witr key sath tera rakatein marvi (riwayat hui) hain, aur kam sey kam no rakatein."
445,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab raat mein tahajjud nahin padh paatey they aur neend is mein rukawat bin jati ya aap par neend ka ghalba ho jata to din mein (uskey badle mein) baara rakatein padhtey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Saad bin Hisham hi ibne Aamir Ansari hain aur Hisham bin Aamir Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key as-haab (saathiyon) mein sey hain. Behaz bin Hakeem sey riwayat hai ke Zarara bin Aufi Basra key qazi they. wo bani Qushair ki imaamat kartey they, unhoney eik din Fajr mein aayate kareema (‏فإذا نقر في الناقور * فذلك يومئذ يوم عسير ) ''jab soor phunka jaeyga to wo din sakht din hoga.'' padhi to wo behosh ho kar gir padey aur mar gaey. main bhi un logon mein shamil tha jo unhen utha kar unke ghar ley gaey."
446,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah taala har raat ko jab raat ka pehla tihai hissa guzar jata hai padhi. aasmane duniya par utarta hai padhi. aur kehta hai : main badshah hun, kon hai jo mujhey pukarey taake main uski pukar sunoon , kon hai jo mujh sey maangey taake main usey dun, kon hai jo mujh sey maghfirat talab karey taake main usey maaf kar dun. wo barabar isi tarah farmata rehta hai yahan tak ke Fajr roshan ho jati hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Ali bin Abi Talib, abu-Saeed , Rifaa Juhni, Juber bin Mut-im , ibne-Masood , Abu Dardaa aur Usman bin Abi al-Aas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain 2- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 3- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey ye hadees kaee sanadon sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai, 4- isi ke saath aap sey ye bhi riwayat ki gaee hai ke aap ney farmaya : ''Allah taala jab waqt raat ka aakhiri tihai hissa baqi reh jata hai utarta hai.''  aur ye sab sey ziyada sahih riwayat hai,"
447,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : ''main (tahajjud key waqt) tumharey paas sey guzra , tum Quran padh rahey they, tumhari aawaz kuchh dheemi thi?'' kaha : main to sirf usey suna raha tha jis sey main munaajaat kar raha tha. (yani Allah ko) aap ney farmaya : ''apni aawaz kuchh buland kar liya karo.''  aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : ''main tumharey paas sey guzraa, tum Quran padh rahey they, tumhari aawaz bahut oonchi thi?''  kaha : main sooton ko jagaata aur shetan ko bhagaa raha tha. aap ney farmaya : ''tum apni aawaz thodi dheemi kar liya karo.''.Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Aaisha , Umme-Haani , Anas , Umme-Salma aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- isey Yahya bin Is-haq ney Hammad bin Salma sey musnad kiya hai aur ziyada tar logon ney ye hadees Sabit sey aur Sabit ney Abdullah bin Ribah sey mursalan riwayat ki hai. (yani : Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ka zikr nahin kiya hai.)"
448,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam eik raat Quran ki sirf eik hi aayat khadey padhtey rahey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai.
449,"Mainey Ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey puchha : raat mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki qirat kaisi hoti thi kya aap Quran dheerey sey padhtey they ya zor sey? kaha : aap har tarah sey padhtey they, kabhi sirri padhtey they aur kabhi jahri, to mainey kaha : Allah ka shukar hai jisney Deen key mamley mein kushadgi rakhi hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
450,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tumhari namaz mein sab sey afzal namaz wo hai jisey tum apney ghar mein padhtey ho, siwaye farz key.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein umr bin Khattab , Jabir bin Abdullah , abu-Saeed , Abu-Hurera , ibne-Umar , Aaisha , Abdullah bin Saad , aur Zaid bin Khalid Juhni (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- ehle-ilm mein is hadees ki riwayat mein ikhtilaf hai, Musa bin Aqba aur Ibrahim bin Abi Nazar dono ney Isey Abu-Nazar sey marfooan riwayat kiya hai. isi ke saath isey Malik bin Anas ney bhi Abu-Nazar sey riwayat kiya, lekin unhoney isey marfoo nahin kiya hai, aur baaz ehle-ilm ney isey maqoof qarar diya hai jabke hadees marfoo ziyada sahih hai."
451,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum apney gharon mein namaz padho padhi. aur unhen qabristaan na banao.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
